{"arkId":"cl010278389","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010278389","modified ":"2025-08-25","title":"Caton","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"D\u00e9nomination","value":"statue"},{"type":"Titre","value":"Caton"}],"displayDateCreated":"Epoque \/ p\u00e9riode : romain imp\u00e9rial\r\n\r\nDate de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 2e moiti\u00e9 IIe s. av. J.-C. ; 2e moiti\u00e9 XVIIIe s. ap. J.-C. (?) (-150 - -100)\r\nDate de r\u00e9utilisation :  (1750)","currentLocation":"N\u00eemes (France), Mus\u00e9e de la Romanit\u00e9, Salle d\u0027exposition","room":"","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":-150,"endYear":-100,"imprecision":"","text":"2e moiti\u00e9 IIe s. av. J.-C. ; 2e moiti\u00e9 XVIIIe s. ap. J.-C. (?)","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""},{"startYear":1750,"endYear":"","imprecision":"","text":"","type":"Date de r\u00e9utilisation","doubt":""}],"creator":[],"objectNumber":[{"value":"MR 321","type":"Autre num\u00e9ro d\u0027inventaire"},{"value":"SMD 72","type":"Autre num\u00e9ro d\u0027inventaire"},{"value":"1154","type":"Num\u00e9ro d\u00e9positaire"},{"value":"Ma 4869","type":"Num\u00e9ro catalogue"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Antiquit\u00e9s grecques, \u00e9trusques et romaines","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"homme (tunique, toge, calceus) ; support (capsa) (Togatus de taille humaine, d\u00e9sign\u00e9 comme Caton par l\u0027inscription sur la base orn\u00e9e de guirlandes sur trois c\u00f4t\u00e9s. Debout en appui sur la jambe gauche, v\u00eatu de la toge et chauss\u00e9 de calcei, \u00e0 c\u00f4t\u00e9 de son pied gauche la capsa (coffret cylindrique) sert d\u0027appui. La main gauche (moderne) tenait un volumen ; le bras droit fl\u00e9chi revient sur la poitrine, main sur le coeur, en passant dans le plis en V du balteus form\u00e9 tr\u00e8s haut. T\u00eate frontale aux cheveux boucl\u00e9s, d\u00e9taill\u00e9s en m\u00e8ches isol\u00e9es au tr\u00e9pan, barbe courte en collier, fine moustache. Statue recompos\u00e9e : le portrait ne se rapportait pas \u00e0 l\u0027origine \u00e0 ce corps ; la cuvette d\u0027encastrement pour la t\u00eate est trop large pour le cou. Base semblable \u00e0 celle qui supporte l\u0027autre statue en d\u00e9p\u00f4t dans le m\u00eame lieu (Ma 4870).)\r\n\r\nEtat de l\u0027oeuvre : moins t\u00eate,main gauche\r\nRestauration : refait(mains)-montage moderne(t\u00eate moderne sur corps)","inscriptions":"Inscription : \r ; Caton\r ; Langue : \r ; latine\r ; Nature du texte : \r ; nom propre (contenu du texte-\u003Einscription civile)","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"183","displayDimension":"183 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"60","displayDimension":"60 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Profondeur","value":"43","displayDimension":"43 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""},{"type":"Hauteur","value":"14","displayDimension":"14 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":4,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : marbre (vein\u00e9 de gris)\r\nTechnique : ronde-bosse (sculpture)","placeOfCreation":"","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"Inconnu","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"Ch\u00e2teau des Tuileries","note":"","role":""},{"value":"Collection Royale","note":" (origine incertaine)","role":""}],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"saisie r\u00e9volutionnaire","doubt":"","dates":[]}],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9partement des Antiquit\u00e9s grecques, \u00e9trusques et romaines","longTermLoanTo":"Mus\u00e9e de la Romanit\u00e9, 